			<rich_text>In To Glory and Beyond, the player tkaes control of a Party of adventurers on a quest to vanquish the Evil of the land.

A game consists of building a party, setting out on an adventure to defeat an Evil and finally either Victory or Defeat. Regardless of outcome, the game will have lasting impact on the players upcoming attempts.</rich_text>
